{"tid":1266632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍵盤戰士的自我修養","createTime":"2019-06-29T15:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T15:06:53.000Z","uid":137789,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bdf9ae238242929dc648bbaff4845aa8bacad010","tid":1266632,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"成日話班<span style=\"color: blue;\">鍵盤戰士</span>係連登軍師，有冇諗過冇班真鍵盤戰士喺度頂住，個平台會變成點？鍵盤戰士喺香港就好似IT狗咁，俾人貶到零價值，冇人諗過佢哋嘅value，根本佢哋就係中流砥柱，網絡得以健康成長，全靠有一班鍵盤戰士細水長流咁，日以繼夜嘅付出，一有咩事俾N毛洗版，帶風向，第一時間出嚟頂住，用腦救火嘅，就係呢班平時唔起眼嘅<del>IT狗</del>鍵盤戰士。"},{"pid":"86370818f2e0d9aca65ba073d81fd4bd040a6a61","tid":1266632,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:04:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">各位巴絲頂住呀！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"18b76123cfd2ddec2df09647df7b4e6fe2c4d064","tid":1266632,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:06:50.000Z","msg":"烈士係贏咗先有得追封<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1266099\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1266099</a>"},{"pid":"287989db85ed77ad054d517c9d3f76d6cf8ea121","tid":1266632,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"頂住，記住要團結，關鍵時候大家唔好咁計較"},{"pid":"da2874aad649e3e820418a94af9bbdb453678906","tid":1266632,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:59:54.000Z","msg":"有班驚天犬不斷<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">消費死者</span></strong>同<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">聲稱想死</span></strong>，又係鍵盤戰士出嚟守備嘅時候"},{"pid":"6226d6f1d445406e1f6597030365f0455e2b6bdf","tid":1266632,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:10:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2cfb05d7daeb7a177e8f3f0d43aff3fb02fc1a2a","tid":1266632,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6226d6f1d445406e1f6597030365f0455e2b6bdf","tid":1266632,"u